long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get player info by hovering player's name. 
Have you ever wanted to know more about PDGA member? Find out more about it's membership, rating and events just by hovering the name.
This extension helps disc golfers find more about their next opponent, friend or just a random PDGA member.
